title: 〈美股盤後〉押注銀行危機已過 四大指數連二紅
description: 投資人押注銀行危機已過，以及聯準會可能很快暫停升息的希望增加，美股週四主指 (30 日) 全數收紅，道瓊收漲逾 140 點，連續第二個交易日收高。

title: Why Amazon Stock Shot Nearly 2% Higher Today
description: Amazon (NASDAQ: AMZN) stock was an outperformer on Thursday, rising almost 2% higher against the S&P 500 index's 0.6% gain.  Although Amazon is known chiefly as a direct-to-your-door retailer, the real powerhouse of its business is its cloud computing service.  With that in mind, investors were cheered that the company isn't mixing it up in a fight that seems to be brewing between Alphabet and Microsoft.
